<dl id="n42019c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42019c">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42019c"> 19(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> tail of a cow / in hand saves</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Who has not been filled with deep compassion and pity for those poor idolators of Hindostan, who believe that they will secure to themselves a happy passage to the next life, if they have the good luck to die when holding in their hands the tail of a cow? <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 82</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
